1.en: Earlier in the day, Gibbs' deputy, Bill Burton, had been confident that there would not "be a lot of Supreme Court stuff today. "
1.cn: 当天稍早的时候，吉布斯的副手比尔·伯顿断言否认“今天有很多最高法院的材料。”

2.en: And so, gradually over these three days, you start off kind of trying to figure out, why am I listening to all this irrelevant stuff?
2.cn: 因此，在为期三天的TED会议里，你开始会试图弄明白为什么我要听这些彼此无关的演讲？

3.en: All of that stuff that pops up and distracts you needs to go down on paper (or into your text editor).
3.cn: 所有那些时不时出来干扰你想法的内容都必须被记在纸上，当然也记可以在文字编辑器或是别的什么东西上。

0.en: Yeah. Here's a box of your stuff.
0.cn: 是的，这一盒是你的东西。

1.en: That is exactly why I do not lend you stuff.
1.cn: 所以我才不借给你东西！

2.en: Wow, you really like all this space stuff?
2.cn: 你很喜欢太空的东西，是吧？

3.en: No. Well, I cannot give this stuff away.
3.cn: 不要。呃，这些东西怎么送也送不出去。

4.cn: 这都是成年人的东西，你理解不了的。

5.en: Don't try to make me uncomfortable with feminine stuff.
5.cn: 别想用女人的东西来唬我。

6.en: You know, I've never played my stuff for anyone before.
6.cn: 我的东西没有弹给别人听过。

7.en: It's fun talking to you, Leonard. I always learn stuff.
7.cn: 跟你说话真有趣，莱纳德，总学得到东西。

8.en: What stuff? Monica's chicken parm. I'll take care of it.
8.cn: 什么东西？莫妮卡的奶酪鸡，我得把它解决掉。

9.en: It doesn't go with any of my stuff. Well, what about my stuff?
9.cn: 听着，它与我的东西都不搭配。那么我的东西呢？

10.en: Watch out! Whoa! Oh, my good. A T. Rex. Get your stuff. Get your stuff. Get it.
10.cn: 当心，当心。哦，天啊，霸王龙! 快收拾好东西，收拾好东西，快点。

11.en: I'm sorry. You know, I have to ask for stuff that we really need, stuff that he can get easily.
11.cn: 抱歉，我得要我们真正需要的东西，他很容易就能弄到的东西。

12.en: Excuse me. Do you know anything about this stuff? I know everything about this stuff.
12.cn: 打扰一下，你了解这个东西吗？我了解它的一切。

13.en: What a lot of stuff! We must be careful not to forget anything when we go.
13.cn: 这么多的东西。我们必须小心，别把东西落下拉。

14.en: Hey, what's going on? He got all of his stuff stolen.
14.cn: 怎么了？他的东西全被偷了。

15.en: Let's grab our stuff and get the hell out of here.
15.cn: 我们快把东西拿一拿，离开这里吧。

16.en: Crazy stuff, bragging, crazy stuff, karaoke. No, see, I don't see anything useful here.
16.cn: 极度自恋，疯狂自恋，卡拉OK，不，我在这没得到任何有用的东西。

17.en: Hi. Hi. Hi darling. So, what's this. Some of your old stuff.
17.cn: 亲爱的这是什么？你以前的东西。

18.en: Anyway, are you going to get a handyman to install this stuff?
18.cn: 你要找人帮忙安装这些东西吗？

19.en: Okay. You want to start loading this stuff into the truck?
19.cn: 好吧，要开始把这些东西搬上货车吗？
